productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
I saw one of these in Vanuatu and I bought one.
I saw one of these in Juan de Nova Island and I bought one.
I tried to slay it but got truffle all over it.
